<p style="text-align: center;">Have your soap delivered right to your front door.&nbsp; Our soap membership also makes a great gift.&nbsp; The soap box includes 4 bars of soap that are delivered to your home 3 times per year.&nbsp; Your first membership order will include a free wood soap dish!&nbsp; Every 3 months you will be billed $25.96 and $6.49 for shipping.&nbsp; A total of $32.45 will be charged to a credit card when your Soap Box is mailed.</p>

